{
  "video_id": "eNtQ83buNVg",
  "title": "Why World Cup Balls Look So Weird Every Tournament",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 400.0,
      "end_time": 1819.0,
      "text": "- [Narrator] Everyone knows what a typical"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 1820.0,
      "end_time": 4500.0,
      "text": "soccer ball looks like, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 4500.0,
      "end_time": 6810.0,
      "text": "It's as simple as black and white."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 6810.0,
      "end_time": 8980.0,
      "text": "But that's not exactly what World Cup balls"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 8980.0,
      "end_time": 11000.0,
      "text": "have always looked like."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 11000.0,
      "end_time": 12583.0,
      "text": "So what's the deal?"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 16300.0,
      "end_time": 17660.0,
      "text": "First things first."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 17660.0,
      "end_time": 21440.0,
      "text": "You want a soccer ball to be as spherical as possible."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 21440.0,
      "end_time": 24630.0,
      "text": "- In the old days we had balls that had the"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 24630.0,
      "end_time": 27130.0,
      "text": "bucky ball shape, the Epcot Center shape."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 27130.0,
      "end_time": 31290.0,
      "text": "You had the 20 hexagons and the 12 pentagons."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 31290.0,
      "end_time": 34769.0,
      "text": "And that was a very good approximation to a sphere."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 34770.0,
      "end_time": 39330.0,
      "text": "But starting in 2006, in Germany, with the Teamgeist ball,"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 39330.0,
      "end_time": 41300.0,
      "text": "there were more creative ways to make"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 41300.0,
      "end_time": 43489.0,
      "text": "that approximation to a sphere."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 43490.0,
      "end_time": 45280.0,
      "text": "- [Narrator] New technology enables Adidas"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 45280.0,
      "end_time": 48600.0,
      "text": "to start designing the balls with fewer panels,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 48600.0,
      "end_time": 51200.0,
      "text": "which actually created a serious problem,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 51200.0,
      "end_time": 54840.0,
      "text": "because fewer panels means less seams,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 54840.0,
      "end_time": 58250.0,
      "text": "and, more importantly, a smoother surface."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 58250.0,
      "end_time": 59920.0,
      "text": "- If the ball gets too smooth,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 59920.0,
      "end_time": 63370.0,
      "text": "the air resistance for certain speeds goes up."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 63370.0,
      "end_time": 65110.0,
      "text": "It's like kicking a beach ball."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 65110.0,
      "end_time": 66940.0,
      "text": "- [Narrator] And that's exactly what happened"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 66940.0,
      "end_time": 70130.0,
      "text": "with the 2006 Teamgeist ball."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 70130.0,
      "end_time": 71679.0,
      "text": "Players complained that the ball"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 71680.0,
      "end_time": 74100.0,
      "text": "didn't go where they expected it to."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 74100.0,
      "end_time": 77160.0,
      "text": "So in 2010, Adidas compensated by adding"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 77160.0,
      "end_time": 80420.0,
      "text": "some texture to roughen up the surface."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 80420.0,
      "end_time": 82330.0,
      "text": "Problem solved, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 82330.0,
      "end_time": 84560.0,
      "text": "- Jabulani was a spectacular failure"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 84560.0,
      "end_time": 86293.0,
      "text": "because it was not rough enough."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 86293.0,
      "end_time": 89390.0,
      "text": "When the ball would be kicked at certain speeds,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 89390.0,
      "end_time": 91850.0,
      "text": "you'd notice it would look like it would slow down"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 91850.0,
      "end_time": 93809.0,
      "text": "dramatically in the middle of its flight."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 93810.0,
      "end_time": 96660.0,
      "text": "- [Narrator] And the panels kept disappearing."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 96660.0,
      "end_time": 100300.0,
      "text": "The 2014 ball had the fewest panels yet:"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 100300.0,
      "end_time": 101750.0,
      "text": "six!"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 101750.0,
      "end_time": 104220.0,
      "text": "But this time Adidas compensated."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 104220.0,
      "end_time": 107960.0,
      "text": "- Despite having two fewer panels from Jabulani,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 107960.0,
      "end_time": 110500.0,
      "text": "the total seam length around the ball"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 110500.0,
      "end_time": 114830.0,
      "text": "was actually 68% longer than it was for the Jabulani."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 114830.0,
      "end_time": 116580.0,
      "text": "- [Narrator] So at least this time the ball"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 116580.0,
      "end_time": 118539.0,
      "text": "had the right amount of roughness"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 118540.0,
      "end_time": 122500.0,
      "text": "and flew further than the 2010 ball."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 122500.0,
      "end_time": 124230.0,
      "text": "As for 2018?"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 124230.0,
      "end_time": 126750.0,
      "text": "- Total seam length on this ball,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 126750.0,
      "end_time": 129919.0,
      "text": "it's actually 30% longer than the Brazuca."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 129919.00000000001,
      "end_time": 131700.0,
      "text": "So now you run the risk of the ball"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 131700.0,
      "end_time": 133200.0,
      "text": "being a little too rough."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 133200.0,
      "end_time": 136100.0,
      "text": "- [Narrator] And again, Adidas compensated for this"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 136100.0,
      "end_time": 139000.0,
      "text": "by also making the seams shallower."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 139000.0,
      "end_time": 141100.0,
      "text": "And studies show the Telstar 18"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 141100.0,
      "end_time": 144200.0,
      "text": "performs similarly to the Brazuca."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 144200.0,
      "end_time": 146369.0,
      "text": "But it still has a bit more drag"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 146370.0,
      "end_time": 150310.0,
      "text": "and might not travel as far on high-speed kicks."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 150310.0,
      "end_time": 153460.0,
      "text": "Regardless, all this begs the question:"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 153460.0,
      "end_time": 155980.0,
      "text": "If the goal is to produce a ball that's similar"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 155980.0,
      "end_time": 159100.0,
      "text": "to what athletes practice with for years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 159100.0,
      "end_time": 161810.0,
      "text": "why does the World Cup ball keep changing?"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 161810.0,
      "end_time": 165600.0,
      "text": "Turns out it's not about the players or the game at all."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 165600.0,
      "end_time": 168700.0,
      "text": "I'm sure you can guess what it's all about."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 168700.0,
      "end_time": 170549.0,
      "text": "- There's a new ball released for every World Cup."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 170550.0,
      "end_time": 174250.0,
      "text": "But I think the primary reason is money."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 174250.0,
      "end_time": 176290.0,
      "text": "- [Narrator] The 2018 World Cup ball"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 176290.0,
      "end_time": 178829.0,
      "text": "costs more than a hundred dollars."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 178830.0,
      "end_time": 181300.0,
      "text": "- And these balls fly off the shelves."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 181300.0,
      "end_time": 182440.0,
      "text": "- [Narrator] It's a pretty big investment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 182440.0,
      "end_time": 186620.0,
      "text": "considering you can get a simple replica for 20 bucks,"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 186620.0,
      "end_time": 188640.0,
      "text": "though they're not exactly the same."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 188640.0,
      "end_time": 190790.0,
      "text": "- The technologies involved in these balls"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 190790.0,
      "end_time": 193870.0,
      "text": "are much, much greater than the balls we used as kids."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 193870.0,
      "end_time": 197000.0,
      "text": "The panels on these balls are thermally bonded."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 197000.0,
      "end_time": 200100.0,
      "text": "It helps keep the water out of the inside of the ball,"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 200100.0,
      "end_time": 201690.0,
      "text": "keep the water from making the ball"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 201690.0,
      "end_time": 204730.0,
      "text": "a little water-logged and heavier."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 204730.0,
      "end_time": 206273.0,
      "text": "- [Narrator] But is it worth it?"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 207600.0,
      "end_time": 209299.0,
      "text": "We'll let you figure that one out."
    }
  ]
}